===Idiom===
'''[[there]] [[ought]][[to|ta]] [[be]] [[a]] [[law]]'''
# From ''there [[ought]] [[to]]'' ([[should]]) ''be a law'', a strongly sarcastic phrase said to convey frustration about something, that in particular should never be remedied by government intervention.